{"tid":1370833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食老婆餅要知道既法例","createTime":"2019-07-27T06:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T06:31:21.000Z","uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9706fcf30398bc97925d8479bfb6fd0c4c1a5338","tid":1370833,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:12:23.000Z","msg":"今日突然間好想食老婆餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽人講元朗d老婆餅唔錯<br />\n但買得多又驚俾人查袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話我違法<br />\n不如講下有咩法例可以保障返自己買老婆餅既權利<br />\n<br />\n我淨係記得 <br />\n第50條第6個section <br />\n只可沒收被拘捕人士既老婆餅<br />\n<br />\n仲有無人記得邊條法例 歸納下"},{"pid":"1e53feefa0c3c31e48c7631b6e769a957a1cb440","tid":1370833,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:15:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2db1305cdeaa7bfdcafd3b99f0c2d9709213c9f4","tid":1370833,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:16:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a6494872b54b4413fcfbb1fcf38bf524106c2cbd","tid":1370833,"uid":140726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:19:31.000Z","msg":"好似話買多過兩盒老婆餅要向元朗海關報稅"},{"pid":"ef0c828a7499aa6b18b590577932653a3fdcf2f2","tid":1370833,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:31:21.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"}]}